  "texts": [
    "The results of the assessment using Vicuna as backbone are depicted in Figure 4.",
    "We observe that GPT-4 exhibits the weakest factual consistency, while the original LoRA also shows a comparatively lower level of factual accuracy than FFT.",
    "However, explicitly incorporating RST structure into LoRA mitigates the issue of hallucinations/inaccuracies in generated summaries, achieving better results than FFT model.",
